headline: DuPont Earns Perfect Score in Human Rights Campaign Foundation's 2025 Corporate Equality Index
summary: DuPont (NYSE: DD) today announced it has received a perfect score of 100 on the Human Rights Campaign Foundation's 2025 Corporate Equality Index (CEI), the nation's foremost benchmarking survey and report measuring corporate policies and practices related to LGBTQ+ workplace equality.
